short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open GitHub Repositories in Google IDX Instantly.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows you to quickly open or import GitHub repositories into Google IDX. 
If you've previously imported a repository, it will automatically open in IDX.

The popup displays your imported repositories for quick access. All data is stored locally in your browser.
